commit.message:
Makefile.am (EXTRA_DIST): Bring up to date.

2007-04-11  Paolo Bonzini  <bonzini@gnu.org>

	* Makefile.am (EXTRA_DIST): Bring up to date.
	* Makefile.in: Regenerate.
	* src/frv/eabi.S: Remove RCS keyword.

From-SVN: r123776
